reviews.review_text: s1 vg, skip s2 Playing-wise, Set 1 is very good, but set 2 starts to fall apart a few songs in and is really a careless mess.
was there i loved the show- they are (were) all different

NotThere, but all 4/30 shows deserve a listen like, in my book any 4/30 show is important, historically, for the Vietnam Vets, and for those who remember history. 4/30 is a date that will be remembered in infamy. Try 4/30/84 if a clear SBD is out there, for sure. Its harsh but perfect.
